I presume that you are running a cable from the line outputs of the
bass and guitar amps into line-level inputs on your FOH mixer.

How you eq those inputs first and foremost is whatever it takes to get
the sound you want. I end up rolling off the top end and bottom end,
and putting in a peak in the upper bass (bass) or lower midrange
(guitar)

